INSERT INTO
    fuel_estimates (
    fiskeridir_vessel_id,date,estimate,status
   )
SELECT
    *
FROM
    UNNEST(
        $1::BIGINT[],$2::DATE[],$3::DOUBLE PRECISION[],$4::INT[]
    )
        ON CONFLICT (fiskeridir_vessel_id, date) DO UPDATE SET estimate = EXCLUDED.estimate,status = EXCLUDED.status
